@Node Shortcuts "Organiser Help: Keyboard Shortcuts"
@ToC Main
@{B}Keyboard Shortcuts@{UB}

Keyboard shortcuts are used to speed up your productivity with
Organiser by providing keyboard alternatives to using the mouse.


@{fg highlight}Commands@{fg text}

KEY                COMMAND
Right Amiga A      Save As
Right Amiga C      Cut
Right Amiga D      Duplicate
Right Amiga E      Edit Details
Right Amiga F      Find
Right Amiga G      Find Again
Right Amiga H      Hide
Right Amiga J      Go To Date
Right Amiga M      This Month
Right Amiga N      New
Right Amiga O      Open
Right Amiga P      Print
Right Amiga Q      Quit Organiser
Right Amiga S      Save
Right Amiga T      Today
Right Amiga V      Paste
Right Amiga W      This Week
Right Amiga X      Cut
Right Amiga Z      Undo
Right Amiga ?      About
       Ctrl E      Create Diary Event
       Ctrl A      Create Address
       Ctrl T      Create Task

Del                Erase
Help               Help Contents


KEY                COMMAND
Shift R. Amiga-E   Edit Details (alternate Address requester)
Shift R. Amiga-J   Go To selected date
Shift R. Amiga-M   Next Month
Shift R. Amiga-T   Tomorrow
Shift R. Amiga-W   Next Week
    Shift Ctrl-A   Create Address (alternate requester)
       Shift Del   Erase (without confirmation)


@{B}Views@{UB}

KEY                DOES
Space Bar          At a Glance
1, 2, 3            Change Address View
1, 2, 3, 4         Change Diary View


@{B}Navigating@{UB}

KEY                DOES
,                  Previous Page

.                  Next Page

Tab                Next Section

Shift-Tab          Previous Section


@{fg highlight}In a Requester@{fg text}

Select any gadget in a requester by pressing the underlined
letter of the gadget title. When editing a text gadget, hold
down the Ctrl key and then press the underlined letter.

KEY                DOES
Ctrl-Return or
Enter (Keypad)     Selects default button (shown in bold),

Esc (Escape)       Cancels requester,

Tab                Moves to next text gadget,

Shift-Tab          Moves to previous text gadget,

Return             Accepts text gadget entry.


@{B}Editable Popups or Active Scrolling Lists@{UB}

KEY                DOES
Down Arrow         Move to next item in list

Up Arrow           Move to previous item in list

Shift-Up Arrow     Move to previous page in list

Shift-Down Arrow   Move to next page in list

Alt-Up Arrow       Move to first item in list

Alt-Down Arrow     Move to last item in list
@EndNode



